text: Â @J BÂ  "active"??? Bro they have been on a hiatus for almost 5 years since 2017. This is not active at all lol. And they were definitely destroyed. The incident occurred in 2012 and it took 4 years for this scandal to be resolved. I think you need to do proper research, T-ARA's incident has got to be the worst in KPOP history. All the members received death threats, they received a black ocean during their performance, a petition to kick them out of the industry got over 200,000 signatures, knetz said one of the members who got into a car accident should have died in it. The entire Korea hated them, it was unimaginable. From then on, Korea has no longer supported them, the reason they still continued to make a lot of money was solely because of their Chinese fans. T-ARA is incredibly famous in China. T-ARA will never get their success and popularity back. If that scandal never happened, they would have been on the same level as SNSD right now. I believe you're underestimating this incident.

text:
Â @hanichannÂ  Â  back when T-ARA was one of the top tier groups ( tied to Girls generation and 2ne1) haters basically claimed that T-ARA's members bullied hwayoung (she was a new member back then)
It was started when T-ARA had their first independent show in japan. Hwayoung claimed to suffer a serious leg injury 2 days prior to their show. When they arrived in Japan, hwayoung was walking normally until people started to take photos of her. Doctor stated that her leg was fine but she insisted on getting a cast and wheelchair.
On the first day of the show hwayoung only performed one song while sitting down. After the show ended, the original members tweeted about determination. This is when people speculated that they bullied hwayoung. Hwayoung and her twin sister milking this by playing victim. The allegation got so out of control with haters and hwayoung stans pulled out false evidences based on incomplete variety show clips and small accidents (e.g when hyomin accidentally poked hwayoung's face)

The only way to clear out the scandal was that hwayoung explained to the public.
However, she kept playing victim and people fell for it. T-ARA was being dragged for bullying
